OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: What were the
OL,4,Ckey dates for the North East?
OL,6,FITV Tyne Tees presenter Amy Lea looks
OL,7,Fback at how the miners' strike
OL,8,Funfolded from the Marches of 1984-1985
OL,10,FIt has been 40 years since Britain's
OL,11,Fmineworkers downed tools - bringing
OL,12,Fone of the country's biggest
OL,13,Findustries to a halt.
OL,15,FThe miners' strike of 1984 saw most of
OL,16,Fthe nation's 200,000 miners walk out
OL,17,Fin what would become one year of
OL,18,Faction.
