OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: What were the
OL,4,Ckey dates for the North East?
OL,6,FAt its peak, every one of the near
OL,7,F23,000 miners from the coalfields of
OL,8,FNorthumberland and County Durham were
OL,9,Fout on strike.
OL,11,FThat year brought misery and pain to
OL,12,Fthe miners, their families and their
OL,13,Fcommunities - and at times violent
OL,14,Fclashes between workers and police.
OL,16,FDespite this, 12 months of action
OL,17,Fshone a light on the spirit and
OL,18,Fsolidarity of the communities affected.
OL,20,FHere we take a look at the key moments
OL,21,Fof the strike from beginning to end.
